
1. Imagine a person/man

<clothes>
  <outerwear>
    <item>Coat</item>
    <item>Hat</item>
    <item>Glove</item>
    <item>Footwear</item>
  </outerwear>
  <basic-clothes>
    <item>Suit</item>
    <item>Shirt</item>
    <item>Tie</item>
  </basic-clothes>
  <accessory>
    <item>Tie pin</item>
    <item>Cufflinks</item>
    <item>Pocket square</item>
  </accessory>
  <underwear>
    <item>T-shirt</item>
    <item>Panties</item>
    <item>Socks</item>
  </underwear>
</clothes>

2. Traversing structure

- dressing:

--> Underwear --> Basic-Clothes --> Accessory --> Outerwear

- undressing:

--> Outerwear --> Accessory -->Basic-Clothes --> Underwear.